quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  38,62,"Ka bɛ (toondannim’ maa) yεli: “Bo n-leei chɛ ka ti bi nyari ninvuɣu shεba ti ni daa kaandi pahiri ninvuɣu bɛri puuni la?”"
  38,63,"“Di ni bɔŋɔ, ti daa kuli maandi ba la ansarsi (Dunia puuni), bee ti nina n-kuli bi pali ba (buɣum ŋɔ ni)?”"
  38,64,Achiika! Di lala buɣum bihi namgbanpeeni ŋɔ maa nyɛla yɛlimaŋli
  38,65,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yεlima! Achiika! Mani nyɛla saɣisigulana. Yaha! Duuma jεmdigu n-kani ni yεlimaŋli naɣila Naawuni, O nyɛla zaɣiyini, Nyɛŋda"
  38,66,"“Sagbana mini tiŋgbani, n-ti pahi din be di sunsuuni Duuma, Ŋuna n-nyɛ Nyɛŋda, Chεmpaŋlana"
  38,67,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Yεlima: “Di (Alkur’aani) nyɛla lahibali din bara.”"
  38,68,Yinim’ (Larbunim’) mi nyɛla ban lebi biri ka chɛ li
  38,69,N-di ka baŋsim shεli n-zaŋ chaŋ Malaaikanim’ sani saha shɛli bɛ ni daa ŋmεri namgbankpeeni la
  38,70,Bɛ bi siɣsiri wahayi n-tiri ma na m-pahila n-nyɛla saɣisigulana n-tin ya polo ni
  38,71,"(Yaa nyini Annabi)! Teemi saha shεli a Duuma (Naawuni) ni daa yεli Malaaikanima: “Achiika! N (Mani Naawuni) nyɛla Ŋun yɛn nam ninsala ni yεɣari.”"
  38,72,"“Dinzuɣu, N-yi ti nam o naai, ka pɔbsi N nyɛvuli niŋ o ni, yi (Malaaika- nim’) man lum ya, ka nyɛla ban niŋdi suzuuda n-tiri o.”"
  38,73,Ka Malaaikanim’ zaasa lu n-niŋ suzuuda n-ti o namgbaniyini
  38,74,"Naɣila Ibliisa (shintaŋ) n-daa tibgi o maŋa, ka pahi gutulunim’ puuni"
  38,75,"Ka O (Naawuni) yεli: “Yaa nyini Ibliisa (shintaŋ)! Bo n-leei mɔŋ a ni a lu suzuuda ti N-ni nam ni N (Mani Naawuni) nuhi ayi? Di ni bɔŋɔ, a tibgila a maŋa, bee a bela ban duhiri bɛ maŋ’ zuɣusaa puuni"
  38,76,"Ka o (shintaŋ) yεli: “Mani n-gari o, A nam ma mi ni buɣum, ka nam o ni yεɣiri.”"
  38,77,"Ka O (Naawuni) yεli: “Tɔ! Yim di (Alizanda maa) puuni, achiika! A nyɛla bɛ ni kari so yihi N nambɔzɔhigu ni.”"
  38,78,“Yaha! Achiika! N narimbu be a zuɣu n-zaŋ hali ni Sanyoodali.”
  38,79,"Ka o (shintaŋ) yεli: “Yaa n Duuma (Naawuni)! Naɣisim ma hali ni dabsi’ shεli Chiyaama ni yɛn ti yiɣisi.”"
  38,80,"Ka O (Naawuni) yεli: “Achiika! A be bɛ ni yɛn naɣisi shɛba ni.”"
  38,81,“N-zaŋ chaŋ sahamirili dali.”
  38,82,"Ka o (shintaŋ) yεli: “M-po A nam nyɛŋsim, achiika! N-nyɛla ŋun yɛn birgi ba namgbaniyini.”"
  38,83,“Naɣila bɛ puuni ban nyɛ A dabgahinda.”